name: Ext_R5_Device_ud_entryType
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.Device.udiCarrier.entryType for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version extension represents Device.udiCarrier.entryType from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/Device|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4B.

element.short: barcode | rfid | manual | card | self-reported | electronic-transmission | unknown
element.definition: A coded entry to indicate how the data was entered.
element.comment: `Device.udiCarrier.entryType` maps to R4B `Device.udiCarrier.entryType`. The value set relationship of SourceIsBroaderThanTarget is INCOMPATIBLE for a required binding on a `code` type in this direction. So is mapped as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget.
